# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Crowe Logic Foundry — REST Client scratch pad (VS Code)
#   Install extension: humao.rest-client
#   Click "Send Request" above any request block below.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@host = http://127.0.0.1:8001
@key  = cl_REPLACE_WITH_ISSUED_KEY

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### List CroweLM model catalog (requires key)
GET {{host}}/api/gateway/models
Authorization: Bearer {{key}}

### Gateway chat — CroweLM Nano (developer tier)
POST {{host}}/api/gateway/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-5.4-nano",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Introduce yourself in one sentence."}
  ],
  "max_tokens": 64
}

### Gateway chat — CroweLM Titan (lab tier)
POST {{host}}/api/gateway/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-5.4",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "system", "content": "You are CroweLM Titan."},
    {"role": "user",   "content": "Outline a 3-stage mycelium scale-up plan."}
  ],
  "max_tokens": 256
}

### Gateway chat — CroweLM Prime (lab tier, Anthropic-backed)
POST {{host}}/api/gateway/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "claude-opus-4-6",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Give me a one-paragraph overview of Crowe Logic."}
  ],
  "max_tokens": 200
}
